'''龍蝦瘟疫真菌'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Aphanomyces astaci''）是一種會感染[[淡水龍蝦|淡水龍蝦]]的[[水黴|水黴]]，歐洲[[河螯蝦屬|河螯蝦屬]]的生物在感染之後的數個星期內就會死去。[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]、[[新幾內亞|新幾內亞]]和[[日本|日本]]的龍蝦也有感染的可能。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pac.dfo-mpo.gc.ca/sci/shelldis/pages/cpfdcy_e.htm |title=Crayfish plague (fungus disease) |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081212165759/http://www.pac.dfo-mpo.gc.ca/sci/shelldis/pages/cpfdcy_e.htm |archivedate=2008-12-12 |publisher=[[Fisheries_and_Oceans_Canada|Fisheries and Oceans Canada]] |accessdate=June 29, 2011 |author=Susan M. Bower |date=June 28, 2006 |work=Synopsis of Infectious Diseases and Parasites of Commercially Exploited Shellfish |deadurl=yes }}</ref>被[[國際自然保護聯盟|國際自然保護聯盟]][[物種存續委員會|物種存續委員會]]的入侵物種專家小組（ISSG）列入[[世界百大外來入侵種|世界百大外來入侵種]]。

==分佈==
1859年龍蝦瘟疫真菌首次出現在歐洲的[[意大利|意大利]]，當時的寄主可能是進口自北美的一些龍蝦，<ref name="Nellemann">{{cite book |editor=Christian Nellemann & Emily Corcoran |year=2010 |title=Dead Planet, Living Planet: Biodiversity and Ecosystem Restoration for Sustainable Development |publisher=[[United_Nations_Environment_Programme|UNEP]] / [[Earthprint|Earthprint]] |isbn=978-82-7701-083-0 |chapter=Restoration of a depleted crayfish fishery in Europe – lessons learnt |page=90–91 |chapterurl=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=irLBX-3nBEQC&pg=PA90 |url=http://www.unep.org/pdf/RRAecosystems_screen.pdf |format=[[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]]}}</ref> 也可能是來自[[壓艙水|壓艙水]]。<ref>{{cite book |editor=Erkki Leppäkoski, Stephan Gollasch & Sergej Olenin |year=2002 |title=Invasive Aquatic Species of Europe: Distribution, Impacts, and Management |publisher=[[Springer_Science+Business_Media|Springer]] |isbn=978-1-4020-0837-5 |author=Kei Westman |chapter=Alien crayfish in Europe: negative and positive impacts and interactions with native crayfish |pages=76–95 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=KkQoxh2oXc8C&pg=PA76}}</ref> 隨後這種真菌便迅速傳播到了整個歐洲。

==描述==
感染龍蝦瘟疫真菌的龍蝦尾部會變成白色或紅褐色。<ref name="Buller">{{cite web |title=Crayfish Plague |author=Nicky Buller |url=http://www.scahls.org.au/__data/assets/pdf_file/0004/1516513/Crayfish_Plague.pdf |format=[[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]] |work=Australia and New Zealand Standard Diagnostic Procedure |date=September 2008 |publisher=Sub-Committee on Animal Health Laboratory Standards |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140126181114/http://www.scahls.org.au/__data/assets/pdf_file/0004/1516513/Crayfish_Plague.pdf |archivedate=2014-01-26 }}</ref> 雖然這種真菌原先的寄主，即產自北美的[[通訊螯蝦|通訊螯蝦]]對其有抵抗力，<ref name="Nellemann"/> 但至今仍沒有任何歐洲的龍蝦可以在感染此真菌後存活。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.europe-aliens.org/pdf/Aphanomyces_astaci.pdf |format=[[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]] |title=''Aphanomyces astaci'' |author=David Alderman |date=December 18, 2006 |accessdate=June 29, 2011 |work=Delivering Alien Invasive Species Inventories for Europe |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924003638/http://www.europe-aliens.org/pdf/Aphanomyces_astaci.pdf |archive-date=2015-09-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="EA"/> 其孢子對溫度變化敏感。

==措施==
爲了防止龍蝦瘟疫真菌的蔓延，歐洲許多水產業部門都對區域間運輸時攜帶的水（例如壓倉水）有一定限額。同時规定在使用进口龍蝦作釣餌時，必须事先經過{{convert|-10|C|F}}以下低溫對其进行至少一天的冷凍處理。龍蝦瘟疫真菌的孢子在短短几周內就可以蔓延到整個水域，並感染當地龍蝦。<ref name="EA">{{cite web |url=http://www.environment-agency.gov.uk/subjects/fish/246986/342184/1205879/1205996/?lang=_e |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080921083819/http://www.environment-agency.gov.uk/subjects/fish/246986/342184/1205879/1205996/?lang=_e |archivedate=2008-09-21 |publisher=[[Environment_Agency|Environment Agency]] |title=Crayfish plague |accessdate=June 29, 2011 |date=June 2, 2011 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

